imdb.plot outline: Airshow Extreme is a new series of heart pounding, death defying stunts, with highlights of all types of aircraft rarely seen in this detail. World War II fighter jets, open air prop planes, modern day war birds, and air show regulars the Thunderbirds, to name a few, take us on a mission that is guaranteed to fascinate and thrill.
